 What is Euler's Theorem tell us for the case when N equal P times Q,

2
00:00:04,260 --> 00:00:06,390
 where P and Q are prime numbers?

3
00:00:06,390 --> 00:00:09,105
 For any Z which is relatively prime to N,

4
00:00:09,105 --> 00:00:12,245
 which means that the GCD of Z and N is one,

