 and we're going to use this P_minus_one, Q_minus_one,

12
00:00:38,305 --> 00:00:42,151
 to generate a encryption key and the decryption key,

13
00:00:42,151 --> 00:00:45,080
 and this is going to give us a basic fact,

14
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:48,885
 which is going to allow the encryption and decryption.

